  <entry>
    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Provisioning Profile Tips &amp; Tricks]]></title>
    <link href="http://skabber.github.com/provisioning-profile-tips-and-tricks/"/>
    <updated>2012-12-10T00:42:00-07:00</updated>
    <id>http://skabber.github.com/provisioning-profile-tips-and-tricks</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Use this command to verify a .mobileprovision file and output its contents.
<code>
openssl smime -in /path/to/your.mobileprovision -inform der -verify
</code>
If you are on Linux you may not have Apples Cert installed into openssl so you can use
<code>
openssl smime -in /path/to/your.mobileprovision -inform der -verify -noverify
</code></p>
]]></content>
